claim.claim-text:
1. A shaving-mirror apparatus, comprising:
an open top, wherein the open top is configured to attach to a bottom of a round shaving-cream container;
a side wall;
a bottom portion, wherein the bottom portion comprises a mirror; and
a layer of material, wherein the layer of material is positioned above the mirror and across an inside bottom of the open top.

8. A shaving-mirror apparatus to place onto a bottom of a shaving-cream container, comprising:
an open top;
a bottom; and
a side wall;
wherein the bottom comprises a mirror;
wherein the open top comprises an inside bottom;
wherein the inside bottom of the open top comprises a layer of material directly above the mirror; and
wherein the open top is configured to attach to the bottom of the shaving cream/gel container.

14. A shaving-mirror apparatus to place onto a bottom of a shaving-cream container, comprising:
a receptacle, wherein the receptacle comprises a bottom, a side wall, and an open top;
wherein the bottom of the receptacle comprises a mirror;
wherein the open top is configured to engage with the bottom of the shaving-cream container.
